pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: hiw-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 60, 400, 24]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>HOW IT WORKS</p>

  - elementId: hiw-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 90, 600, 50]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      fontSize: 36
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Three steps to strategy</p>

  - elementId: hiw-step1-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 220, 80, 60]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 48
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>01</p>

  - elementId: hiw-step1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 290, 320, 36]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 24
      color: "$text"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Build the board</p>

  - elementId: hiw-step1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 336, 320, 180]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.7
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Add stakeholders with nicknames, roles, and stances. Pick from 55 traits across 6 categories — Big Five, communication, politics, decisions, and motivators.</p>

  - elementId: hiw-line1
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [420, 260, 40, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$secondary"}
    arrow: [null, "arrow"]

  - elementId: hiw-step2-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 220, 80, 60]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 48
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>02</p>

  - elementId: hiw-step2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 290, 320, 36]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 24
      color: "$text"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Write your move</p>

  - elementId: hiw-step2-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [480, 336, 320, 180]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.7
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Describe the proposal, pitch, email, or initiative you're about to launch. Add observed behavior notes and payoff structures — what each player gains or loses if you succeed.</p>

  - elementId: hiw-line2
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [820, 260, 40, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$secondary"}
    arrow: [null, "arrow"]

  - elementId: hiw-step3-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [880, 220, 80, 60]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 48
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>03</p>

  - elementId: hiw-step3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [880, 290, 320, 36]
    content:
      fontFamily: "HedvigLettersSans"
      fontSize: 24
      color: "$text"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Run the simulation</p>

  - elementId: hiw-step3-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [880, 336, 320, 180]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 18
      lineHeight: 1.7
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Get private reads, likely moves, objections, and counters for each player. Plus a board-level strategic read — the one move that shifts the most payoffs in your favor.</p>

  - elementId: hiw-line
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [80, 680, 1120, 0]
    shapeName: straightConnector1
    border: {style: solid, width: 1, color: "$primary"}

  - elementId: hiw-brand
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1020, 688, 180, 22]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      fontSize: 11
      letterSpacing: 2
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>THE WAR ROOM</p>